data.description: Private Tree Lined Backyard on Almost Half an Acre! New Tile Just Installed in the Kitchen & Guest Bathroom! Hardwood Flooring in the Living Room, Hallway and All Bedrooms! Spacious Living Room with a Wood Burning Fireplace & High Ceiling! Kitchen Features Tile Backsplash, an Upgraded Sink & Upgraded Appliances Including a Samsung Flex Double Oven & Black Stainless Steel French Door Refrigerator! Primary Bedroom Has a Trey Ceiling, Double Vanity, Jetted Tub & a Walk-in Closet! Amazing, Fenced in Backyard Features a 24ft Above Ground Pool, a Large Deck with an Awning, Lots of Mature Trees & No Backyard Neighbors! Washer, Dryer, & Ring Doorbell & Alarm System Stay! A Must See!
